# Violin
# V, Warmup
# Focus: [pickMemK(`focus`, `intonation tone`)]
{stops=`thirds, fourths, sixths, octaves`;}
{shapes=`dim sixths ysaye tonic squares`;}
{modes=`1 2 3 4 5 6 7`;}
-=- scales
Scales3-{ss(`ion dor phry lyd mix aeo loc`)}: [key] three octaves
ScalesClimb: [key], [pick('dia, dia, dia, dia, dia, dim, whole')], climb on: [ss(`GDAE`).join('')] / [ss(`pos 1-4s ` + ss(`12 21 123 231 312`).slice(0, 2)).join(` `)]
{after('2026-04-05', '')} ScalesPos: [key] [scalePositions()]
-=- scale-stops
ScaleStopsRun: [key] [pick(stops)] [ss(`1234`)]
ScaleStopsPart: [key] [pick(stops)] [scalePositionsDbl()]
ScaleStopsString: [key] [pick(stops)] [zipSpace(ss(`DAE`).slice(0, 2), ss(`0+H-W+H, 0+W-H, 0+H-W+H, 0+W-H`))] [ss(`1234`)]
-=- bowing
0x Bowing-{ss(modes)}: [key]
Bowing-{ss(shapes)}: [key] run
0x Bowing-{ss(shapes)}: [key], p{divide(zip(ss(`1234`), shuffleX(s(`uudd`), 2), shuffleX(s(`â†‘â†‘â†“â†“`), 2)), 1)}
ArtificialHarmonics: vibrate [ss(`GDAE`)] [ss(`up down`)]
BowingBackIntoWall: shoulder blades together [ss(`snake, scale, ysaye`)]
-=- shifting
#{after('2026-03-16', '')} ShiftingFourth: [key] position 4 [(`octaves from 1st, shifts 1-4 ${ss(`0 -1 +1`).join(' ')}, shifts interleaved`)] [ss(`G D A E`)]
0x ShiftingSlides: [key] [(ss(`GDAE`).map(s=>chromaticSlide(key, s))).join(', ')]
ShiftingSlides: quartertone [key] [(ss(`GDAE`).map(s=>chromaticSlide(key, s))).join(', ')]
{after('2026-04-05', '')} ShiftingSevcik: [key] Sevcik, no gliss [ss(`G D A E`)]
ShiftingSnake: [key] position: [ss(`2 3 4 5 6 7`)], [ss(`G D A E`)]
SemitoneFrame: [ss(`GDEA`)] +[ss(`1 2 3 4 5 6 7`)]sem [ss(`lyd maj, min, phyr, `)]
ShiftingAgainstWall: [ss(`snake, scale, ysaye`)]
--- dims
Dim-{pickNKeys('dims', 12).map(s=>s.replace(/#/, 's'))}: play
# V, Technique
--- extensions
# Ext1: 4 finger: [zip(shuffleX(`3rd/, 4th/, 4#/, 5th/`, 2), ss(scalePositions({arrows: false})))]
--- bowings
# Bowing1: sautille, {ss(`DG AD EA`).map(str => str + ` ` + ss(`40 31 22 13`).join(':'))}
Bowing2: E-G connection [divide(shuffleX(`GEu EGd`, 4), 2).join(' | ')] (arches)
Bowing3: marcato with control over [pick(shapes)], p{divide(ss(`1 2 3 4 5 6`), 2)}
Bowing4: fast draws [pick(shapes)]
Bowing5: contact point randomization (circles)
--- stops
Stop1: Bowing: 4-stops
Stop2: Bowing: sixths on EA, GD intersperesed 
Stop3: Fingerboard: sixths: sliding fingers over fifths, flat pads
--- entrances
Entr1: bow ends clicks exercise [ss(`GDAE`)]
Entr2: entrances in tips [ss(`GDAE`)]
Entr3: entrances down, with stability and power
