# Piano
# P, Exercises
--- piano-exercises
{maybeEvery(5, 'ExerciseMin251: ' + j(pickNKeys('minor', 3)) + ', ' + j(ss(`24 36 24 36`).slice(0, 3)))}
{maybeEvery(3, 'ExerciseMaj251: ' + j(pickNKeys('major', 3)) + ', ' + j(ss(`32 7b5 32 7b5`).slice(0, 3)))}
{maybeEvery(`3,1`, 'ExerciseFlipflops: 35/34' + j(pickNKeys('flipflops', 3)))}
{maybeEvery(`4,1`, 'ExerciseStepwiseDia: ' +  pick(`5 6 7 56 34 24`) + ': ' + j(pickNKeys('chords-diatonic', 3)))}
TriadPairs: 1 & 2 (write parametrization)
# Comping: {ss(`shell 3, shell 7, 37, 73, rootless 2, rootless 5, call letters`)}
HWLicks: pick three
Scale-alt: play alt resolutions (678910 is flat)
ChromaticBassline: try accompanying
