Oleo: [ss(`head-metred, two-free-runs, comping`)]
BirksWorks: [ss(`head-metred, solo-1-metered, solo-2-metered`)]
BluesForAlice: [ss(`head-metered, comping, two-free-runs`)]
Blue-Train: play
JazzFutter: play
GluckAccomp: play
Entertainer-page{ss(`A B1 B2 C D`)}: with metronome
